name: Aliens...S
description:
Aliens...S

(the S stands for spaceship...)

  In the year 2429, war broke out with an Alien race. Decades later it is up to you to "keep them away" for as long as possible.

  This will result in your death but if you survive long enough and kill enough enemies, humanity might survive.

Make sure to read the README included for controls and credits.

This game was made in 72 hours for Ludum Dare 50.
